value.0: Harbingers of blood and death in the frozen north, the mighty white dragon is often confused with a stupid animal. The Wyrm Frostspear makes short work of those whom would make such a grave mistake. Her piercing eyes are as sharp as her talons, her fangs like steel icicles which rend the flesh of any beast - or any man. When you hear her roar, take heed: you have become her prey.
OOC ring for all bosses, to protect against the more popular spells for instant death.
With a roar of ice and snow, the cave entrance has sealed behind you. You can't get out!
